### create blog post

POST http://localhost:3001/api/blog/post HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "author": "Peter Parker Again",
    "title": "Title Example",
    "text": "This is sample text for a blog post!"
}

### get blog post

GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog/6330d707b1d8142515b2b011


### get all blogs

GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog


### create comment

POST http://localhost:3001/api/blog/post/comment/6330d707b1d8142515b2b011 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
    "author": "Commenter Name",
    "text": "Nice post! This is another random comment",
    "postId": "6330d9d48fc801265d290458"
}


### get all comments for ID

GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog/post/comment/6330d9d48fc801265d290458 HTTP/1.1

### get all comments no matter the id

GET http://localhost:3001/api/blog/post/comment HTTP/1.1